  <brief_title>An Educational Intervention Based on the Teach Back Method on Self-care Practice Among Menopausal Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of an Educational Intervention Based on the Teach Back Method on Self-care Practice Among Menopausal Women</official_title>
